e a corresponding\nentry in `c.steps`, return `none`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.DynStructureM.Context.updateMVarIds\"><span class=\"name\">Aesop</span>.<span class=\"name\">DynStructureM</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">updateMVarIds</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(c : <a href=\"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.DynStructureM.Context\">Aesop.DynStructureM.Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(map : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/HashMap.html#Lean.HashMap\">Lean.HashMap</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">Lean.MVarId</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">Lean.MVarId</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.DynStructureM.Context\">Aesop.DynStructureM.Context</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/aesop/blob/53ba96ad7666d4a2515292974631629b5ea5dfee/Aesop/Script.lean#L253-L253","name":"Aesop.DynStructureM.instInhabitedContext","line":253,"kind":"instance","docLink":"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.DynStructureM.instInhabitedContext","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.DynStructureM.instInhabitedContext\"><span class=\"name\">Aesop</span>.<span class=\"name\">DynStructureM</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedContext</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.DynStructureM.Context\">Aesop.DynStructureM.Context</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/aesop/blob/53ba96ad7666d4a2515292974631629b5ea5dfee/Aesop/Script.lean#L252-L252","name":"Aesop.DynStructureM.Context.steps","line":252,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.DynStructureM.Context.steps","doc":"The tactic invocation steps corresponding to the original unstructured\nscript, but with `MVarId` keys adjusted to fit the current `MetaM` state. This\nstate evolves during dynamic structuring and we continually update the `steps`\nso that this map's keys refer to metavariables which exist in the current\n`MetaM` state. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.DynStructureM.Context.steps\"><span class=\"name\">Aesop</span>.<span class=\"name\">DynStructureM</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">steps</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(self : <a href=\"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.DynStructureM.Context\">Aesop.DynStructureM.Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/PersistentHashMap.html#Lean.PHashMap\">Lean.PHashMap</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">Lean.MVarId</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.TacticInvocation\">Aesop.TacticInvocation</a></span>)</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/aesop/blob/53ba96ad7666d4a2515292974631629b5ea5dfee/Aesop/Script.lean#L246-L246","name":"Aesop.DynStructureM.Context.mk","line":246,"kind":"ctor","docLink":"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.DynStructureM.Context.mk","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Aesop/Script.html#Aesop.DynStructureM.Context.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Aesop</s